==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wordish
<hw>Word"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Respecting words; full of words;
wordy.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <au>Sir P. Sidney.</au> --
<wordforms><wf>Word"ish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The truth they hide by their dark <qex>woordishness</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Sir K. Digby.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wordle</ent>⟦br⟧
